      "content": "i get what u mean about the serotonin but honestly i'm just so tired of feeling like this and i can't really afford a doctor's appointment right now with student budget stuff. if i just stick to a very low dose of the st johns wort, like just a tiny bit extra, is it really gonna be that bad? it's just a plant, it shouldn't be that different from the sertraline which is already working okay-ish. i just want that extra edge for studying.",
